@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Our Story";
    Layout = "_Layout2";
}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css"/>

<!-- ✅ Inter font (same family as your Blog page styling) -->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
    /* 1. THE CRITICAL FIX - PREVENTS NAVBAR OVERLAP */
    .page-wrapper { 
        padding-top: 120px; 
        background-color: #ffffff;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1; 
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .story-container { 
        max-width: 850px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        padding: 0 20px 80px; 
    }

    /* 2. MATCHED BLOG TYPOGRAPHY */
    .motive-label {
        color: rgb(29, 43, 54);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        opacity: 0.6;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.35rem; /* ✅ closer to Blog hero spacing */
    }

    /* ✅ MAIN HEADING FIX (match Blog hero heading) */
    .story-heading {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-size: 2.5rem;       /* same as Blog hero h1 */
        font-weight: 700;        /* same "fw-bold" feel */
        color: rgb(29, 43, 54);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: 0;       /* Blog heading is clean */
    }

    .narrative-text {
        font-size: 1.05rem; /* Matched to Blog Body */
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(29, 43, 54, 0.85);
    }

    /* 3. THE MOTIVE CARD (EMPHASIS) */
    .motive-highlight {
        margin: 50px 0;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        background: rgba(29, 43, 54, 0.03);
        border: 1px dashed rgba(29, 43, 54, 0.2);
    }

    .motive-highlight h4 {
        color: rgb(29, 43, 54);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.4rem; /* Matched to Blog Subheaders */
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .signature-line {
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        background: rgb(29, 43, 54);
        margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .motive-footer {
        background: rgb(29, 43, 54);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .motive-footer h5 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }
</style>

<div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="story-container">
        
        <span class="motive-label">Our Story</span>
        <h1 class="story-heading">From Financial Clutter to <br>Mathematical Clarity.</h1>
        
        <div class="narrative-text">
            <p>We started with a simple observation: most people don't lack money—they lack a clear picture of where it goes. In an era of instant digital payments, wealth often vanishes in "micro-leaks" that go unnoticed until the end of the month.</p>
            
            <p>Our journey began with the goal of building a tool that doesn't just list transactions, but tells a story. We wanted to create a platform where every logged expense contributes to a larger report, turning raw numbers into visual logic.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-line"></div>

        <div class="motive-highlight">
            <h4>Our Motive</h4>
            <p class="narrative-text mb-0">Our core motive is to replace financial anxiety with data-driven confidence. By providing a clean interface for tracking expenses and watching goal progress bars grow, we help users transition from passive spending to active wealth building.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="narrative-text">
            <p>We believe that when goals are visible, they are achievable. Our reporting system is designed to highlight your wins and identify your habits, ensuring that your financial milestones are always within sight.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="motive-footer mt-5">
            <h5 class="mb-3">The Objective</h5>
            <p class="small opacity-75 mb-0">To provide the most transparent, goal-oriented tracking experience for the modern saver.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
